data.title: Partners
data.meta_description: Discover partners that are ready to assist you in realizing greater value through Expertise-based services.
data.text:
Accenture

Together, Accenture and Oracle are redefining our partnership to accelerate the path to value for our joint customers.

Deloitte

In a world of continuous change, next is closer than you think. Your next big idea, your next iteration and your next competitive advantage. Accelerate next. Deloitte and Oracle can show you how.

IBM

Accelerate your journey to Oracle Cloud and transform with IBM’s cognitive and automation solutions, tailored by industry and business process domain.

Infosys

Infosys, a leader among Oracle service providers, can accelerate your cloud journey with the help of Infosys Cobalt cloud offerings.

PwC

PwC is a recognized leader in Oracle implementations with an industry-first strategy, helping customers accelerate value realization from their cloud investment.

TCS

TCS is an IT services, consulting, and business solutions organization that has been partnering with many of the world’s largest businesses in their transformation journeys for over 55 years.
